plt.figure(figsize=(5,3),dpi=150)
plt.hist(
    Y.flatten().numpy(),
    range=(-17.5,17.5),
    bins=35,
    density=True,
    width=0.8);
plt.title("Histogram of latents")
plt.xticks(range(-15,16,5));
```


    
